TI  - ENVIRONMENTAL FACTORS CONTROLLING THE EVOCATION AND TERMINATION OF DIAPAUSE IN THE FRUIT TREE RED SPIDER MITE METATETRANYCHUS ULMI KOCH (ACARINA: TETRANYCHIDAE)
